name: The Uranai 4: Harapeko Kuma no Kaiun Kabbalah Uranai
overview: The Uranai 4: Harapeko Kuma no Kaiun Kabbalah Uranai is the fourth games in the Uranai series of Tarot games made for the Playstation One Console. In these games that player provide personal information for the game to make a tarot of the player's personality. After that the player controls the character with his personality through a journey.
